 * 
</P>
<P>
 Oakland Athletic Manager Tony La Russa signed a three-year contract extension, 
including an option to cut the deal short if the A's are sold. Financial terms 
were not disclosed. . . . The Seattle Mariners extended the contract of Manager 
Lou Piniella through the 1996 season. 
</P>
