Pizza in Orange, Scarlet Lady Saloon in Culver City, Sports Harbor in Culver 
City, Texas Loosey's in Torrance and in Fullerton, The Alibi Room in Culver 
City, The Landing Strip in Van Nuys and Warehouse in Newport Beach. 
