<HEADLINE>
<P>
COMMUNITY NEWS FOCUS: BUENA PARK; COUNCIL CANDIDATES FORUM SET FOR TONIGHT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By LESLEY WRIGHT 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Residents will be able to shoot questions at their City Council candidates 
during a forum at 7 p.m. tonight in the Council Chambers at 6650 Beach Blvd. 
</P>
<P>
 Each of the eight candidates will have three minutes to read a prepared 
statement, and audience members may ask questions afterward. 
</P>
<P>
 Comcast Cable will carry the forum live on Channel 53 and will repeat the 
broadcast from 8:30 to 10:30 p.m. every Wednesday, and from 10:30 a.m. to 12:30 
p.m. every Sunday until the election. 
